high_descs: Turn left then walk toward the center table
Pick up the credit card on the center table
Turn left then head to the left side of the sofa
Put the credit card on the sofa beside the pillow
Turn right then head to the right side of the tv stand
Pick up the credit card on the tv stand
Turn left then head to the end of the sofa
Put the credit card on the sofa
anns.task_desc: Put two credit card on the sofa

high_descs: Walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the coffee table.
Pick up the red credit card off of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk up to the left side of the couch.
Put the red credit card on the couch under the blue pillow.
Turn right and walk over to the wall, then turn left and walk up to the television.
Pick up the red credit card that is on the table in front of the television.
Turn left and walk across the room to the left side of the couch.
Put the red credit card on the seat of the couch behind the blue pillow.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards to the seat of the couch.

high_descs: Step forward, then turn left and in the space between the table and TV. Turn left to face the table.
Pick up the credit card to the left of the box.
Turn left, go forward, then turn right and to the edge of the couch.  Turn right to face the couch.
Place the credit card underneath the blue pillow on the couch.
Turn right and walk to the edge of the TV stand.
Pick up the credit card on the TV stand.
Return to the edge of the couch.
Place the credit card on the couch behind the other credit card.
anns.task_desc: Find two credit cards and place on the couch.
